# Smart Garage

Self-hosted vehicle management (Next.js, **SQLite**, Docker, Unraid).

**New chat:** read `AGENTS.md` at repo root before non-trivial work.

## Stack

- **App:** `frontend/` — Next.js 16 App Router, TypeScript strict, React 19
- **i18n:** next-intl — English default, German; **no hardcoded UI text**
- **Data:** SQLite + Prisma 6 (`frontend/prisma/`)
- **Deploy:** single Docker image → GHCR; data on `/data` volume

## Docs (current)

| Doc | Purpose |
|-----|---------|
| `AGENTS.md` | **Agent onboarding + pitfalls** |
| `README.md` | User-facing overview |
| `docs/UNRAID.md` | Unraid install |
| `docs/INSTALL.md` | Backup, updates |
| `CHANGELOG.md` | Releases |

Do **not** reference removed files: `ARCHITECTURE.md`, `ROADMAP.md`, `DATABASE.md`, `DEVELOPMENT.md`, `PROJECT.md`.

## Code rules

- TypeScript in `frontend/` — no `.js` source files
- UI strings in `messages/en.json` + `messages/de.json` only
- Business logic in `lib/domain/` and `lib/services/` — no React imports
- Data access in `lib/repositories/` — Prisma only
- Authorization in services — never UI-only checks
- Validate with Zod at boundaries
- Do not commit `.env`, secrets, or `data/`

## Out of scope unless requested

- New features without explicit task
- PostgreSQL (project uses SQLite)
- Restoring deleted internal docs
